item.title: Song
item.description: Mere Khuda Intro I know the way I walking was wrong, That you were never with me oh my God! And now I want to edify my thoughts, cause, You will be my destiny, My destiny. Bekarar he, Betab he, Bejaan si yeh jindagi, Betaal me kyun chal rahi? Ae Khuda…. tu he kaha? Meri aashaa, mera jahaan… Verse 1 Tujhe dhundta he, Saara jahan ye, Par phir bhi kyun na tu mila he inhe?
